t violations. This technical report is updated\ncontinuously as modifying, adding, and deleting constraints remains ongoing\nwork.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2015 10:43:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 12 Sep 2015 13:46:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 15 Sep 2015 07:58:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-16"}
