her positive or negative, in contrast to the\nintuition based on the helicopter theory, which suggests positive excess lift.\nThis effect is attributed to unsteady wing-wake interactions. A similar effect\nis found during hovering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Apr 2015 11:44:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2015 05:54:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2016 03:14:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-30"}
